name: "mono-gateway"
version: "%%VERSION%%"
origin: "sysutils/mono-gateway"
comment: "Mono Gateway board support package (NXP LS1046A)"
desc: <<EOD
Board-specific kernel modules, userspace tools, configuration files,
and boot scripts for the Mono Gateway Development Kit.

Includes DPAA1 CDX flow offload (cdx, fci, auto_bridge, pf_notify),
hardware drivers (emc2302, ina2xx, lp5812, sfpled), FMan configuration
tools (fmc, dpa_app), connection management (cmm, cmmctl), and fan
control (fand).
EOD
